title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.29 - All moving aircraft to proceed with running lights between sunset and sunrise
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.29 - All moving aircraft to proceed with running lights between sunset and sunrise

State Regulations

All aircraft being taxied, towed or otherwise moved at
the air terminal shall proceed with running lights on during the hours between
sunset and sunrise. Notes
